WEBVTT

00:55.263 --> 00:56.264
Yes?

00:56.347 --> 00:59.350
Your dad found out. You should run away.

01:08.902 --> 01:10.070
I'll call you back.

01:20.080 --> 01:23.541
EPISODE 14

01:32.509 --> 01:34.427
I'll drop Eun-u off at home first.

01:34.511 --> 01:36.554
No, I'll just get out here.

01:42.101 --> 01:43.561
Are you really going to run away?

01:45.522 --> 01:46.773
I need to save myself first.

01:47.607 --> 01:50.401
Stay on my tail, okay?

02:01.454 --> 02:02.497
Goodness.

02:18.888 --> 02:20.265
I need to get going. I'll call you.

02:21.266 --> 02:22.267
What?

02:23.268 --> 02:24.394
Ji-ho...

02:58.803 --> 02:59.637
My goodness.

02:59.721 --> 03:01.264
Jeong-in?

03:01.598 --> 03:02.932
What are you doing here?

03:04.309 --> 03:05.977
Hey. What's with the photos?

03:06.436 --> 03:07.770
How should I know?

03:07.854 --> 03:09.898
It was from an anonymous sender.

03:11.274 --> 03:13.484
- Where's Dad?
- Just leave.

03:13.568 --> 03:16.237
Leave if you want to live.

03:16.321 --> 03:17.906
I've already braced myself for this.

03:17.989 --> 03:20.283
Jeong-in, wait! Gosh, what do I do?

03:23.745 --> 03:24.829
Explain yourself.

03:27.457 --> 03:30.251
Explain what's in these photos.

03:32.253 --> 03:33.504
It's as you see.

03:34.756 --> 03:36.007
He has a child.

03:38.927 --> 03:41.054
- What the hell are you--
- I'm going to marry him.

03:42.388 --> 03:44.807
Jeong-in, this isn't the time or place--

03:44.891 --> 03:46.017
There's never a good time!

03:46.643 --> 03:48.853
You're not in your right mind, are you?

03:49.437 --> 03:51.648
You're telling us,
instead of asking for our permission?

03:52.148 --> 03:53.858
How is this appropriate?

03:54.317 --> 03:56.945
- We're your parents--
- If I ask,

03:57.570 --> 03:58.571
will you approve?

03:59.864 --> 04:01.032
You've totally lost it.

04:01.115 --> 04:04.744
Jeong-in, you're being too one-sided.

04:04.827 --> 04:08.206
You need to give us time
to think about this too.

04:08.957 --> 04:10.583
I know that your answer is no.

04:11.125 --> 04:13.586
What point is there in thinking
when you've made your decision?

04:14.504 --> 04:15.546
I'm glad you said that.

04:16.547 --> 04:18.841
The fact that you know we'd disapprove

04:18.925 --> 04:22.595
means you know
just how absurd this idea is!

04:23.429 --> 04:25.723
You're right. It's absurd.

04:27.225 --> 04:29.519
I didn't think I'd be like this either.

04:30.478 --> 04:33.815
Sometimes, I even catch myself in a daze.

04:34.857 --> 04:37.443
I think to myself,
"How did this even happen?"

04:39.362 --> 04:40.363
But you know what?

04:41.656 --> 04:42.699
I've never once

04:43.908 --> 04:45.034
regretted this.

04:46.160 --> 04:47.954
It's why I proposed to him first.

04:55.670 --> 04:58.047
- Bring him home.
- No.

04:59.507 --> 05:02.093
Why not? You said you'll marry him.

05:02.176 --> 05:05.763
I know you're planning to
humiliate him and drive him away.

05:06.389 --> 05:07.515
So lash out at me.

05:08.641 --> 05:10.059
I'll gladly take the beating,

05:11.060 --> 05:12.270
but I won't bring him over.

05:29.078 --> 05:30.997
- Hello?
- It's Jae-in.

05:31.456 --> 05:33.791
My mom isn't picking up,
so I have no idea what is going on.

05:33.916 --> 05:35.668
I'm on my way there though.

05:37.420 --> 05:38.629
I'm outside the house.

05:40.089 --> 05:44.135
Don't tell me you're planning to go in.
Don't you dare. My dad will kill her.

05:45.970 --> 05:47.138
You don't

05:48.056 --> 05:49.348
have to date Gi-seok.

05:53.061 --> 05:54.020
Fine.

05:55.063 --> 05:57.148
I'll give up the job at the foundation
after I retire.

05:59.317 --> 06:00.359
What?

06:01.694 --> 06:03.780
I'll give up what I want as well.

06:05.907 --> 06:06.866
I'm sorry,

06:08.034 --> 06:08.993
but I can't give him up.

06:10.328 --> 06:11.704
Jeong-in.

06:12.205 --> 06:16.084
You're only thinking about yourself.
Don't be stubborn about this.

06:16.250 --> 06:19.003
Also, you should
take some time to think it over.

06:19.087 --> 06:20.379
Think about what?

06:20.713 --> 06:22.131
This isn't happening.

06:22.215 --> 06:24.383
The possibility of it happening is zero!

06:24.467 --> 06:28.262
Honey, please!
We can give her our opinions,

06:28.763 --> 06:30.223
but the choice is hers.

06:30.681 --> 06:31.766
Why do parents exist?

06:32.433 --> 06:34.519
We're not supposed to
just watch from the sidelines.

06:34.852 --> 06:36.813
We shouldn't boss them around either.

06:36.896 --> 06:37.897
Stop it.

06:39.565 --> 06:40.983
I know I'm hurting you two.

06:42.360 --> 06:43.569
I'm really sorry.

06:48.449 --> 06:50.368
I don't want to hurt you,

06:52.662 --> 06:54.330
and I'm truly sorry.

06:55.331 --> 06:56.499
But I...

06:57.667 --> 06:58.835
I can't control my feelings.

06:58.918 --> 07:02.672
That's because even though you act tough,
you're too soft inside.

07:03.589 --> 07:05.049
You can put an end to this,

07:05.133 --> 07:08.136
but you're hesitating
because you're worried about others.

07:08.886 --> 07:10.054
What's so hard about this?

07:10.555 --> 07:12.306
- Just suck it up and--
- Don't!

07:34.662 --> 07:38.207
You've been fidgeting with your phone
for a while now.

07:38.291 --> 07:39.417
Are you waiting for a call?

07:41.544 --> 07:42.545
No.

07:45.214 --> 07:48.009
You're drinking faster than usual too.

07:48.426 --> 07:49.510
Something's up, right?

07:52.138 --> 07:53.598
You're the one with news.

07:54.932 --> 07:56.767
Tell me. How does it feel to be a father?

07:58.978 --> 08:00.771
You just completely changed the subject.

08:05.735 --> 08:08.738
Well, I guess it hasn't sunk in yet.

08:11.532 --> 08:12.617
However,

08:13.534 --> 08:15.995
although I feel pressured,
I also feel reassured.

08:17.079 --> 08:18.706
It's like nothing can faze me now,

08:20.458 --> 08:21.834
and I can face just about anything.

08:29.133 --> 08:31.302
Is that what children mean to parents?

08:34.597 --> 08:36.849
If you want to know, go and get married.

08:38.351 --> 08:40.228
Stop talking about it and take action.

08:47.652 --> 08:50.279
You only say that you'll help me as well.

08:54.867 --> 08:55.952
I'm kidding.

09:00.623 --> 09:02.333
Honestly, how was it when you got married?

09:03.668 --> 09:04.835
What do you mean?

09:05.503 --> 09:07.922
- It's just us here.
- Come again?

09:10.258 --> 09:14.178
It's not like you and Seo-in
were madly in love, right?

09:18.683 --> 09:20.810
It'll just stay between us, so tell me.

09:22.270 --> 09:24.689
You know how Jeong-in has been

09:26.315 --> 09:28.234
snippy lately.

09:31.070 --> 09:33.239
I'd like for you to help me
get my head in the game.

09:34.115 --> 09:36.117
How determined do I need to be
to marry someone?

09:44.625 --> 09:47.169
Maybe I should elope with her.

09:49.630 --> 09:50.631
Why not?

09:52.425 --> 09:53.634
It sounds solid, right?

09:58.639 --> 10:00.516
- Did Jeong-in call?
- No.

10:01.309 --> 10:02.560
Shit.

10:03.060 --> 10:05.187
- I'll call you when I know something.
- Wait.

10:06.314 --> 10:07.732
I don't care what it is.

10:07.815 --> 10:09.775
I'll wait here, so please call me.

10:13.154 --> 10:14.196
Enter your passcode.

10:15.156 --> 10:16.574
The door is opening.

10:21.662 --> 10:23.748
Either the phone will crack
or you'll crush your hand.

10:23.831 --> 10:25.166
One is bound to happen.

10:38.763 --> 10:40.181
- Jeong-in.
- Jeong-in?

10:41.265 --> 10:43.351
You can't just leave like this.

10:43.434 --> 10:44.727
What else is there for me to say?

10:45.394 --> 10:47.897
Your father has every right
to be upset about this.

10:48.064 --> 10:50.608
I know,
and I never said I did right by him.

10:51.067 --> 10:52.943
- But Dad--
- What about me?

10:53.944 --> 10:56.155
Do you even have any idea
how much anger I'm holding back?

10:56.989 --> 10:58.866
What kind of humiliation is this?

10:59.325 --> 11:02.244
How can I face Mr. Kwon tomorrow?

11:02.953 --> 11:05.289
Was it him who sent the photos?

11:05.373 --> 11:06.666
Isn't it obvious?

11:07.625 --> 11:09.043
What did I tell you before?

11:09.418 --> 11:11.962
How on earth have you been
conducting yourself?

11:12.630 --> 11:14.924
Mr. Kwon figured it out as well!

11:18.177 --> 11:21.263
Now, there won't be a chance for you
to get back together with Gi-seok.

11:21.889 --> 11:22.932
Good.

11:23.766 --> 11:25.810
- Why you little--
- Honey, please!

11:25.893 --> 11:27.311
- Ji-ho's downstairs.
- Move!

11:28.813 --> 11:29.855
Dad, let's talk this out.

11:29.939 --> 11:31.857
- Dad, no violence.
- Get out of my way!

11:32.358 --> 11:33.692
- Jeong-in!
- Jeong-in!

11:33.776 --> 11:34.902
- Dad!
- Jeong-in!

11:35.903 --> 11:37.446
It's all useless.

11:37.530 --> 11:39.281
In this world, only money counts.

11:39.365 --> 11:41.200
It holds all the power.
That's just how it is.

11:42.910 --> 11:44.078
Damn.

11:45.955 --> 11:47.581
What can't money buy?

11:52.169 --> 11:55.047
Money can even buy love and affection.

12:01.178 --> 12:02.638
That's just sad though.

12:05.224 --> 12:06.684
Let me be honest with you then.

12:09.019 --> 12:10.020
Why...

12:12.064 --> 12:14.108
Why do you think
I wanted to expand the clinic?

12:16.694 --> 12:19.447
For my patients? No, that's nonsense.

12:22.491 --> 12:24.827
I wanted my wife to be able to

12:25.953 --> 12:28.289
brag about her husband.

12:28.372 --> 12:29.874
Am I being cocky? No.

12:31.750 --> 12:33.002
Truth be told,

12:35.004 --> 12:36.088
it's love.

12:39.008 --> 12:40.301
It's due to my love for her.

12:44.930 --> 12:47.475
Then you should've pushed forward.

12:47.850 --> 12:49.310
Why did you scrap the plan?

12:53.439 --> 12:54.732
You piece of jerk.

12:55.483 --> 12:58.235
It was you who didn't grant me the loan.

13:03.949 --> 13:05.993
When I inherit my dad's building,

13:06.410 --> 13:07.953
I'll rent you an office, free of charge.

13:09.747 --> 13:11.499
Wait, is that favoritism?

13:11.582 --> 13:13.834
Fine, I'll only take
a million won a month.

13:19.298 --> 13:21.884
Still, we must become a family first.

13:25.638 --> 13:28.390
- You're hilarious.
- I'm not joking.

13:34.772 --> 13:36.148
Please tell Seo-in

13:36.857 --> 13:39.235
to persuade Jeong-in for me.

13:40.945 --> 13:42.363
If we end up getting married,

13:42.988 --> 13:44.740
I'll make it worth your while.

13:55.209 --> 13:56.502
I'm asking you once again.

13:58.420 --> 13:59.588
I sincerely mean it.

14:05.261 --> 14:07.346
You do seem more sincere this time.

15:46.612 --> 15:49.823
Do you know what
I'm most grateful for after meeting you?

15:52.952 --> 15:54.119
I'm happy

15:55.329 --> 15:57.498
to have someone I can put before myself.

16:00.417 --> 16:01.418
That...

16:02.628 --> 16:03.462
and courage.

16:06.799 --> 16:07.925
You've always been brave.

16:10.928 --> 16:12.304
I thought so too,

16:13.180 --> 16:15.474
but I've only been pretending to be.

16:19.144 --> 16:20.187
On the other hand,

16:21.689 --> 16:24.149
you're going through an ordeal
because of me too.

16:27.152 --> 16:28.445
You said so yourself.

16:29.822 --> 16:31.198
That we shouldn't make excuses

16:31.281 --> 16:33.158
saying we're leaving
for the other person's sake.

16:35.744 --> 16:37.037
I guess I dug my own grave again.

16:40.958 --> 16:43.377
I like that you're brave and courageous,

16:45.004 --> 16:48.424
but lean on me just like you're doing now.
Literally and emotionally.

16:50.384 --> 16:52.803
I want to be someone
who can be there for you.

16:59.893 --> 17:02.771
Then I'll keep on leaning on you.
Don't you take it back.

17:10.738 --> 17:13.699
Your father's words
must've hurt you today.

17:23.208 --> 17:25.085
I guess I brought that on you.

17:31.258 --> 17:32.509
Don't be too stressed out by it.

17:34.928 --> 17:36.013
No matter what others say,

17:37.014 --> 17:38.515
we share the same fate now,

17:41.185 --> 17:42.686
so it's wrong to be hurt by them.

17:46.648 --> 17:47.649
You're right.

17:49.234 --> 17:50.194
You really are.

17:53.530 --> 17:54.615
See?

18:03.082 --> 18:04.166
Let me hug you.

18:05.292 --> 18:06.919
No, let me hug you instead.

18:32.694 --> 18:35.280
The smaller portions are for Jeong-in.

18:36.073 --> 18:38.200
Don't leave them outside her door.

18:38.534 --> 18:39.868
Make sure to put it in her fridge.

18:41.829 --> 18:43.580
Aren't you even angry about this?

18:43.956 --> 18:45.666
Why would you want to pack her food?

18:50.379 --> 18:51.547
What did Dad say?

18:52.131 --> 18:53.507
Isn't it obvious?

18:58.095 --> 19:00.681
They're in love, so just let them be.

19:02.683 --> 19:04.560
Don't you ever become a parent.

19:07.271 --> 19:09.731
Do you know why Seo-in suggested
you meet Ji-ho?

19:10.983 --> 19:12.860
Of course, I know what she meant.

19:13.735 --> 19:15.654
She said that because he's a decent man.

19:17.197 --> 19:19.241
Soon, Seo-in will be a single mother.

19:21.994 --> 19:23.787
Would you be okay

19:24.788 --> 19:26.123
if others pointed fingers at her?

19:29.501 --> 19:31.545
I just don't know anything anymore.

20:36.318 --> 20:37.778
I sorted out those we need to return.

20:38.195 --> 20:40.197
I'm going over the products
that don't sell.

20:42.449 --> 20:43.784
What did you do over the weekend?

20:45.452 --> 20:46.536
Nothing much.

20:48.288 --> 20:50.123
Who are you trying to fool?

20:51.708 --> 20:52.751
What?

20:54.544 --> 20:55.587
What's this about?

20:56.129 --> 20:58.173
You always wash your coat on the weekend,

20:58.257 --> 20:59.508
but it was just left here.

21:00.968 --> 21:02.594
I forgot to take it home.

21:03.387 --> 21:04.554
What's with the interrogation?

21:06.431 --> 21:08.642
That response tells me
that something happened.

21:09.017 --> 21:11.311
Nothing happened,
I was just with Jeong-in.

21:11.395 --> 21:12.479
Hey.

21:13.230 --> 21:15.107
- Can you move, please?
- Only for a cost.

21:15.649 --> 21:16.733
What do you mean?

21:17.484 --> 21:19.278
I'm going to tell your mother.

21:20.153 --> 21:21.363
You're unbelievable.

21:33.292 --> 21:34.418
Yes, Ms. Go.

21:34.668 --> 21:37.129
Ms. Wang, do you have time to talk?

21:37.546 --> 21:39.256
Yes, of course. Go ahead.

21:40.173 --> 21:43.552
Please don't tell Ji-ho that I called.

21:44.261 --> 21:46.513
Well, I'm alone right now.

21:47.472 --> 21:48.473
I see.

21:49.558 --> 21:53.437
There's just something
I've been wanting to ask you in person.

21:55.397 --> 21:57.899
I can't believe
that people actually do this.

21:58.859 --> 22:00.402
I'm just as fascinated.

22:03.196 --> 22:05.282
Is this how the rich and famous operate?

22:06.533 --> 22:08.702
Anyway, what are you going to do?

22:08.952 --> 22:10.412
Aren't you going to go after Gi-seok?

22:11.121 --> 22:12.122
Could it be his doing?

22:12.998 --> 22:15.500
Isn't it obvious? He still wants you back.

22:16.168 --> 22:17.294
He's too proud

22:17.377 --> 22:20.005
to hire a private investigator.

22:20.088 --> 22:21.882
Then why isn't he giving up on you?

22:23.300 --> 22:26.470
Actually, his pride is probably
why he can't let you go.

22:26.887 --> 22:30.432
"If I send this,
Jeong-in's father will be outraged,

22:30.807 --> 22:33.143
and she'll come back to me."

22:33.560 --> 22:34.394
That's his scenario.

22:35.896 --> 22:37.647
But then I'll find out that

22:37.898 --> 22:39.441
he was the one who sent the photos.

22:40.108 --> 22:42.235
You're right.
It'll make you hate him even more.

22:43.570 --> 22:46.323
If it wasn't Gi-seok,

22:47.324 --> 22:48.784
who could've done such a thing?

22:49.659 --> 22:50.952
Gi-seok's father.

22:51.536 --> 22:52.454
No way.

22:52.954 --> 22:54.873
Even my dad assumed that.

23:02.631 --> 23:04.633
- It's me.
- What do you want?

23:06.843 --> 23:07.928
Nothing.

23:08.553 --> 23:09.846
I thought we could grab dinner.

23:11.348 --> 23:12.474
Where should we meet?

23:16.853 --> 23:17.979
Why aren't you speaking?

23:18.939 --> 23:20.232
You said you'd always comply.

23:21.399 --> 23:22.734
Fine. Let's meet.

23:25.112 --> 23:27.531
- Where?
- At your father's house.

23:30.325 --> 23:33.078
I need to talk to your father.
It's best if you're there,

23:33.912 --> 23:34.955
so be there.

23:42.003 --> 23:43.088
Do you have a moment?

23:43.713 --> 23:45.966
For a meal?
Can I order something expensive?

23:46.925 --> 23:48.093
I'd like a word.

23:49.344 --> 23:50.595
We'll talk after Ye-seul leaves.

23:57.310 --> 23:59.271
- Aren't you heading home?
- I will.

23:59.896 --> 24:02.691
You should get going.
I need to scold Ji-ho.

24:06.403 --> 24:08.905
Did I make a mistake as well today?

24:10.240 --> 24:11.783
I can make something up

24:11.867 --> 24:13.410
if you'd prefer to stay.

24:13.660 --> 24:14.828
See you.

24:17.164 --> 24:18.456
- See you tomorrow.
- Bye!

24:23.920 --> 24:26.590
- Did you have to make her worry?
- You're worse.

24:27.465 --> 24:28.675
You're making me nervous again.

24:39.644 --> 24:41.271
Jeong-in asked me to marry her.

24:42.355 --> 24:44.816
Hold on. She proposed to you?

24:46.067 --> 24:50.113
Wow, luck just rolled your way, didn't it?

24:50.906 --> 24:51.907
I know.

24:53.200 --> 24:55.076
I don't know what to do now though.

24:55.619 --> 24:57.537
In terms of marriage?

24:58.747 --> 24:59.831
Our parents.

25:02.250 --> 25:05.086
What did she say? That you should
push through even without their consent?

25:05.170 --> 25:06.296
That's absurd.

25:07.464 --> 25:10.342
It may be disrespectful,
but there's no rule against it.

25:12.469 --> 25:13.595
I know what's going on.

25:14.221 --> 25:17.349
If you try powering through,
they'll think you're insolent

25:17.432 --> 25:20.310
and your pride can't allow that.

25:21.186 --> 25:24.481
However, you're worried
that Jeong-in will leave you

25:24.564 --> 25:26.942
if you wait until both parents approve.

25:27.484 --> 25:29.486
How's that for a summary?

25:31.571 --> 25:34.366
I want to meet her parents,
but I'm worried.

25:34.908 --> 25:36.076
Worst case scenario?

25:36.868 --> 25:40.163
I might cause
an irreparable rift between them.

25:45.085 --> 25:48.046
Instead of holding back
to protect someone,

25:48.797 --> 25:51.174
wouldn't you regret it less if you showed

25:51.258 --> 25:53.218
how far you're willing to go
for that someone?

26:00.433 --> 26:02.227
It really won't take long.

26:02.894 --> 26:03.979
Okay, I get it.

26:04.980 --> 26:06.356
I thought you understood.

26:08.900 --> 26:10.193
This is the last time though.

26:11.236 --> 26:12.237
What do you mean?

26:14.406 --> 26:15.699
This is about us.

26:16.533 --> 26:17.993
We'll do it together from now on.

26:19.286 --> 26:22.080
All right. Just this once then.

26:23.790 --> 26:26.001
I knew I met a woman too brazen.

26:26.710 --> 26:29.087
It seems like
you're already regretting it.

26:30.380 --> 26:31.798
What if I get dumped soon?

26:32.590 --> 26:33.967
Don't you think about running away.

26:35.427 --> 26:36.720
Why would I

26:37.512 --> 26:38.763
when you told me to lean on you?

26:39.556 --> 26:41.683
I will cling onto you like a leech.

26:43.351 --> 26:44.394
Please do.

26:47.522 --> 26:50.984
I'm not as stressed out as you think.

26:53.320 --> 26:54.696
I can take even more than this.

26:56.573 --> 26:57.574
Me too.

27:00.118 --> 27:03.288
Then why don't we bet on it?

27:04.289 --> 27:05.498
We'll see who's stronger.

27:07.375 --> 27:08.460
I'll probably win.

27:09.544 --> 27:10.962
Now my blood's boiling.

27:12.005 --> 27:14.174
The bet is on.
Loser grants the winner a wish.

27:15.759 --> 27:17.135
Can I name my prize first?

27:19.012 --> 27:20.347
You think you've already won.

27:21.598 --> 27:22.682
What is it?

27:24.184 --> 27:25.518
Until we die,

27:26.936 --> 27:28.229
we'll remember each other.

28:03.264 --> 28:04.224
No, don't cross.

28:11.981 --> 28:13.441
I don't think it's a good idea.

28:40.552 --> 28:43.596
I'm very happy that you're not
across the street right now.

28:44.556 --> 28:47.600
PHARMACIST

29:14.210 --> 29:16.379
Hi, come in and have a seat.

29:18.381 --> 29:19.466
Tell her to make some tea.

29:19.549 --> 29:22.010
There's no need.
This will only take a few minutes.

29:23.428 --> 29:26.389
What is it about? I wonder why
you couldn't even tell Gi-seok.

29:27.182 --> 29:28.808
He seemed to have no idea.

29:31.352 --> 29:32.395
Have a seat.

29:59.964 --> 30:01.007
You know what it is, right?

30:05.512 --> 30:07.180
There were some things
I needed to find out.

30:07.263 --> 30:09.682
And you sent it to my parents.

30:15.563 --> 30:16.481
Am I wrong?

30:18.441 --> 30:19.818
Yes, I did.

30:23.363 --> 30:24.405
I'm sorry about that.

30:25.156 --> 30:27.116
No, I should thank you.

30:28.660 --> 30:31.162
I couldn't bring myself
to tell my parents,

30:31.955 --> 30:33.414
but this made me feel relieved.

30:35.333 --> 30:37.460
So you're saying it's true.

30:38.419 --> 30:39.462
Yes, it is.

30:39.546 --> 30:41.923
Hey, did you come all the way here
to say that?

30:42.298 --> 30:43.132
No.

30:44.467 --> 30:46.511
- I'd like the original files.
- Jeong-in.

30:46.761 --> 30:49.639
It was wrong of you to take them,
and I'm uncomfortable that you have them.

30:50.515 --> 30:51.683
I'd like all of them.

30:59.232 --> 31:00.483
Here's my business card.

31:01.693 --> 31:04.737
I know it'll be a hassle,
but please send them to my work address.

31:20.962 --> 31:22.463
You should thank your father too.

31:23.506 --> 31:25.466
You were hoping
my parents would find out soon.

31:26.718 --> 31:28.511
They've found out everything,
as you wished.

31:30.138 --> 31:31.347
I sent those photos.

31:34.142 --> 31:35.393
I didn't want to suffer alone.

31:38.021 --> 31:39.272
There has to be a winner,

31:39.981 --> 31:41.274
no matter how messy it gets.

31:44.319 --> 31:45.361
Do you think

31:46.571 --> 31:48.323
this will make me go back to you?

31:49.282 --> 31:50.575
Ji-ho isn't good enough for you.

31:53.494 --> 31:54.829
Why did you date me?

31:55.872 --> 31:56.873
Why?

31:58.374 --> 31:59.584
Because you loved me so much?

32:03.254 --> 32:05.798
Would you have dated me
even if it hadn't been for my background?

32:09.719 --> 32:10.929
I didn't really care.

32:11.846 --> 32:13.056
Other women are like that too.

32:14.015 --> 32:16.684
I mean,
everyone prefers wealth over poverty.

32:19.354 --> 32:21.064
And I can't say it's not love.

32:37.747 --> 32:38.831
I'm sorry.

32:43.836 --> 32:45.004
It's all my fault.

32:47.173 --> 32:48.758
I betrayed you and broke your heart.

32:50.176 --> 32:51.302
I'm sorry for everything.

32:52.971 --> 32:54.514
I'm not asking you to forgive me.

32:56.015 --> 32:58.226
Even if you curse and pester me
for the rest of my life,

32:59.811 --> 33:02.647
I'll put up with it. All of it.

33:04.691 --> 33:05.858
What's so great about him?

33:07.485 --> 33:09.946
Why would you do all this
just to be with that prick?

33:14.575 --> 33:15.910
I don't need anything else.

33:17.036 --> 33:18.204
There's only one answer.

33:19.539 --> 33:20.707
Just come back to me.

33:22.375 --> 33:23.668
I won't be satisfied with you.

33:25.294 --> 33:26.796
I've gotten greedier.

33:29.924 --> 33:30.967
Jeong-in.

33:37.890 --> 33:39.475
I'm sure you knew,

33:40.226 --> 33:41.894
but I took it without any meaning.

33:43.521 --> 33:44.814
I should've returned it earlier.

34:08.838 --> 34:10.089
If it meant nothing to you,

34:10.173 --> 34:12.341
it's no better than garbage. Right?

34:16.512 --> 34:17.722
I'll say this again.

34:19.307 --> 34:21.309
You'll never be satisfied with Ji-ho.

34:24.145 --> 34:25.188
I should go.

35:28.251 --> 35:30.044
I'm sorry I put you in that position,

35:32.839 --> 35:34.465
but you're partially responsible for this.

35:38.594 --> 35:39.887
And as for Jeong-in...

35:43.099 --> 35:45.476
She's just too compassionate
and tenderhearted.

35:45.977 --> 35:47.520
She's doing this out of pity.

35:49.105 --> 35:50.606
I warned her a few times,

35:51.357 --> 35:52.859
but she kept acting like a child,

35:53.734 --> 35:56.404
so I did it thinking it might be better
for her parents to know.

36:01.284 --> 36:02.368
I'm sorry.

36:11.294 --> 36:12.295
Father.

36:13.588 --> 36:15.006
Don't turn out like me.

38:16.919 --> 38:18.963
I'm so happy
you're just across the street from me

38:20.172 --> 38:21.257
right now.

38:51.370 --> 38:52.997
Again, don't cross.

38:55.499 --> 38:56.834
I'll go to you.

39:27.698 --> 39:30.534
- Could you help me find this book?
- Sure. Just a moment, please.

39:53.349 --> 39:56.185
- Hello.
- Hello, it's been a while.

39:56.644 --> 39:58.771
- Jeong-in is inside.
- It's okay.

39:59.146 --> 40:01.941
I just stopped by because I was in
the neighborhood. Have a nice day.

40:02.316 --> 40:03.401
You too. Bye.

40:13.202 --> 40:14.954
Jeong-in, I just saw your mom.

40:16.038 --> 40:17.456
I guess she had her class today.

40:17.873 --> 40:20.209
- She was peeking in from outside.
- Peeking at what?

40:21.085 --> 40:24.463
I'm not sure.
But the look on her face was a little...

40:25.714 --> 40:26.841
How should I put this?

40:28.259 --> 40:30.136
Shall I say she looked a little sad?

40:31.095 --> 40:32.179
Yes, a little bit.

40:34.515 --> 40:35.474
She left.

40:35.558 --> 40:38.561
I was going to come in and get you,
but she told me not to bother.

40:40.771 --> 40:42.606
Okay. Thanks for letting me know.

40:43.107 --> 40:44.150
No problem.

41:01.625 --> 41:05.963
MOM, I'M SORRY

41:14.221 --> 41:19.477
I'M REALLY SORRY

41:39.830 --> 41:41.790
I know that Jae-in is staying with you,

41:41.874 --> 41:45.461
but we should still apply
for a temporary restraining order first.

41:46.212 --> 41:50.341
If it's issued, he won't be able
to call or even text you.

41:51.300 --> 41:54.303
There are people who choose not to comply
and threaten the applicant,

41:54.678 --> 41:56.889
so I can't say that it's completely safe--

41:56.972 --> 41:57.932
That won't be necessary.

41:58.516 --> 42:00.726
I can handle Si-hoon by myself.

42:01.560 --> 42:03.562
The law is there to help us.

42:03.854 --> 42:06.732
You said he'd end up behind bars
for a couple of years at the most.

42:07.816 --> 42:10.110
Regardless of how it's done,
he should pay for what he did.

42:11.737 --> 42:12.738
I'll get on it right away.

42:14.281 --> 42:15.407
No, it's okay.

42:16.033 --> 42:17.618
Thanks for this consultation.

42:19.245 --> 42:20.412
I'll figure out what to do.

42:25.000 --> 42:27.461
JAYURO LAW FIRM

42:37.054 --> 42:38.013
Now, tell me.

42:38.514 --> 42:40.015
You said you'll figure out what to do.

42:41.517 --> 42:42.810
Don't tell me you'll forgive him.

42:43.602 --> 42:44.645
Of course not.

42:46.105 --> 42:48.315
Like you said,
taking legal action isn't enough.

42:50.693 --> 42:53.112
You're not thinking of
doing something crazy, are you?

42:57.992 --> 42:59.118
Let me do it in your place.

43:01.245 --> 43:02.204
You're pregnant.

43:03.038 --> 43:06.000
That is why I have to do it myself.
Because I'm a mom.

43:06.584 --> 43:08.711
Don't be like this.
You're scaring me here.

43:13.132 --> 43:14.300
Jeez, this startled me.

43:15.759 --> 43:17.845
- Hi.
- Where is the pharmacy?

43:20.848 --> 43:22.266
Mom, what is this about?

43:23.976 --> 43:25.853
Don't tell Jeong-in.

43:27.354 --> 43:29.315
Mom, Jeong-in will kill me.

43:29.898 --> 43:31.025
What is it?

43:44.079 --> 43:46.999
Finally.
I knew you'd get your hands on it.

43:48.709 --> 43:50.210
Is this the power of love?

43:51.795 --> 43:54.923
Okay! How about we have drinks
at my place this evening?

43:55.090 --> 43:58.093
- I'm in, of course.
- I can't join you girls.

43:58.761 --> 44:00.346
I'm going to hang out on the third floor.

44:02.598 --> 44:04.600
I'm seriously going to move.

44:11.982 --> 44:13.025
Come down for a minute.

44:42.554 --> 44:44.348
I stopped by
to talk to you about something.

44:46.642 --> 44:48.185
I have to get back quickly.

44:53.941 --> 44:56.443
What do you want your father to do
after he retires?

45:01.532 --> 45:03.784
My self-esteem has hit rock bottom,
so I can do anything.

45:04.785 --> 45:05.953
This is nothing.

45:08.163 --> 45:10.290
Did I date you
without knowing you well enough?

45:10.999 --> 45:12.376
Or did I make you become like this?

45:13.669 --> 45:14.962
You can beat yourself up later.

45:18.424 --> 45:20.050
What kind of choice should you make

45:20.134 --> 45:21.427
for the sake of you and me

45:21.510 --> 45:24.471
as well as for both of our families?

45:25.764 --> 45:27.224
Think about that first.

45:27.307 --> 45:28.767
That won't be necessary.

45:30.602 --> 45:33.480
Your father now knows
that I left you for another man.

45:34.857 --> 45:36.233
He won't approve of me.

45:38.402 --> 45:40.612
My dad will be too ashamed
to work for the foundation.

45:41.488 --> 45:42.698
Don't give such excuses.

45:46.368 --> 45:49.621
Your dad will join the foundation.
I'll make it happen.

45:54.251 --> 45:55.794
Are you sure you want to win me back?

45:59.631 --> 46:02.509
I even refused to attend the school
where my dad taught.

46:04.636 --> 46:05.888
That's my answer.

46:08.849 --> 46:10.517
I have to get back to work.

46:10.601 --> 46:11.560
Drive safely.

46:27.743 --> 46:29.703
- Here you go.
- Have a nice day.

46:29.786 --> 46:31.288
- Thank you. You too.
- Have a nice day.

46:33.832 --> 46:36.043
WOORI PHARMACY

46:41.965 --> 46:43.008
Did she leave?

46:44.051 --> 46:45.469
You saw the woman outside, right?

46:45.928 --> 46:48.388
She made eye contact with me
a number of times.

46:52.184 --> 46:54.061
Is she here to see Ms. Wang?

46:55.187 --> 46:56.522
Then she would've called her.

46:57.397 --> 46:58.982
By the way, who is Ms. Wang meeting?

47:09.952 --> 47:11.119
One iced Americano, please.

47:12.746 --> 47:14.414
People who don't know the situation

47:15.207 --> 47:17.501
will say that I'm already worrying
too much,

47:18.293 --> 47:19.920
but I can't help it as his mother.

47:21.838 --> 47:23.507
I'm sure you understand.

47:25.008 --> 47:28.387
Going through the whole thing with Eun-u
has helped Ji-ho become maturer.

47:30.806 --> 47:31.765
I know that, but...

47:36.103 --> 47:37.312
Have you heard anything

47:38.689 --> 47:40.107
from Eun-u's mom by any chance?

47:43.360 --> 47:44.361
No, I haven't.

47:44.611 --> 47:48.865
But is it really necessary
to track her down after all these years?

47:50.325 --> 47:52.828
Not knowing her whereabouts
would be best for the both of them.

47:53.912 --> 47:56.373
But what if she shows up one day
and makes unreasonable demands?

47:57.416 --> 48:00.711
Ji-ho finally pulled himself together,
and he's seeing someone now.

48:00.794 --> 48:03.714
- I'm just worried.
- She's not that kind of person.

48:06.925 --> 48:09.011
How could she be so heartless?

48:10.887 --> 48:14.016
I'm not sure how this will sound,
but it's actually a good thing.

48:14.725 --> 48:16.518
She doesn't deserve
to be Eun-u's mom anyway.

48:17.227 --> 48:20.147
The one Ji-ho is seeing now
is not like her at all.

48:20.230 --> 48:21.440
You can trust her.

48:21.523 --> 48:23.317
Here's your iced Americano.

48:23.650 --> 48:25.819
It seems like
Ji-ho completely trusts her as well.

48:26.570 --> 48:28.030
But it's not just about those two.

48:29.031 --> 48:32.326
The problem is
what her family will think about Ji-ho.

48:36.246 --> 48:39.082
If Eun-u is a problem,

48:40.292 --> 48:42.044
I want to tell them that I can raise him.

48:42.878 --> 48:46.256
Ji-ho is Eun-u's dad.
He should do his duty as his parent.

48:46.840 --> 48:50.552
And if they end up getting married,

48:51.011 --> 48:52.971
it'll become
Jeong-in's responsibility as well.

48:55.891 --> 48:57.976
Ji-ho did tell me
that she's a trustworthy person.

48:59.144 --> 49:02.022
It sounded like she comes
from a good family as well.

49:03.273 --> 49:04.900
What if they treat him disrespectfully?

49:07.444 --> 49:08.487
You see,

49:09.321 --> 49:10.822
I'm obviously worried about Ji-ho,

49:10.906 --> 49:14.368
but Eun-u is... That poor thing
didn't even do anything wrong.

49:16.495 --> 49:18.872
He doesn't even know
what his mom looks like.

49:20.624 --> 49:22.209
Just thinking about that breaks my heart.

49:25.045 --> 49:26.088
Ji-ho...

49:26.797 --> 49:28.840
He won't suffer any more heartache.

49:29.341 --> 49:30.884
I trust that he won't.

49:32.886 --> 49:34.930
I can't say with 100-percent certainty,

49:35.180 --> 49:38.975
but I think Jeong-in is
as mentally strong as Ji-ho is.

49:39.059 --> 49:42.020
And most importantly,
the two of them are so similar.

49:42.270 --> 49:44.815
They even act the same way.

49:46.942 --> 49:48.151
- You think so?
- Yes.

49:48.902 --> 49:50.821
I guess they're meant to be.

49:50.904 --> 49:51.905
Yes, exactly.

51:00.974 --> 51:02.017
Excuse me.

51:03.810 --> 51:04.895
Are you Yu Ji-ho's...

51:08.106 --> 51:09.149
Yes.

51:11.526 --> 51:12.360
Are you...

51:13.320 --> 51:14.321
Yes.

51:15.864 --> 51:17.240
I'm Jeong-in's mom.

53:03.805 --> 53:05.724
All right, I'll leave now.

53:08.351 --> 53:09.352
Okay.

53:13.315 --> 53:14.316
Was that your mom?

53:16.067 --> 53:17.277
Yes, she wants me to come over.

53:18.069 --> 53:19.279
What's up with the sigh?

53:20.780 --> 53:22.365
I know exactly what she's going to say.

53:23.408 --> 53:24.826
Jeong-in is probably on her way now.

53:27.537 --> 53:28.830
I met your mom earlier today.

53:32.876 --> 53:34.878
I told her that
you two will get through it together.

53:37.255 --> 53:38.089
And?

53:39.299 --> 53:40.967
She was just worried.

53:47.557 --> 53:49.059
She asked me about Yu-mi.

53:52.395 --> 53:55.440
It just shows how much she likes Jeong-in.
She wants you two to stay together.

53:55.899 --> 53:57.943
When you're very happy
and excited about something,

53:58.568 --> 54:00.403
you get anxious for no reason, you know.

54:00.612 --> 54:02.322
You wonder, "What if things go wrong?"

54:03.031 --> 54:05.700
And moms always worry about everything.

54:08.411 --> 54:09.788
I don't know about others,

54:10.455 --> 54:11.998
but try to understand why she's worried.

54:16.461 --> 54:17.921
It's been six years, for God's sake.

54:18.838 --> 54:20.006
Until when will she worry?

54:23.551 --> 54:24.844
Whenever she does this,

54:24.928 --> 54:27.472
all the painful things I tried so hard
to forget come rushing back.

54:28.765 --> 54:30.892
I know I don't say it,
but I'm worried too.

54:32.143 --> 54:33.728
I'm even terrified at times.

54:35.146 --> 54:37.399
I'm scared she'll show up
and demand Eun-u back.

54:43.530 --> 54:44.739
Yu-mi's married.

54:46.449 --> 54:48.451
I happened to hear about her recently
at a gathering.

54:48.535 --> 54:51.162
Apparently, she even has a kid.

54:54.374 --> 54:55.250
Ji-ho.

55:01.464 --> 55:02.674
I know, Hye-jeong.

55:04.926 --> 55:07.178
I never resented her, and I still don't.

55:08.388 --> 55:09.431
After all,

55:11.474 --> 55:13.101
she gave birth to Eun-u.

55:15.395 --> 55:17.939
Hating her will be like hurting Eun-u,
so I won't do that.

55:19.774 --> 55:20.817
I won't hate her.

55:23.611 --> 55:24.821
You are so cool, Ji-ho.

55:50.263 --> 55:51.473
Let me wipe your face.

55:52.891 --> 55:54.142
All done. Go on in.

56:02.567 --> 56:04.694
He's busy today.
He said he'll come by tomorrow.

56:05.528 --> 56:06.821
Did you tell him you met her mom?

56:07.322 --> 56:09.699
I didn't want to worry him,
so I said nothing about that.

56:11.910 --> 56:13.620
I wonder if something has come up.

56:16.748 --> 56:19.334
Her mom probably told her already,

56:19.959 --> 56:21.836
so he might have heard something.

56:21.920 --> 56:25.090
Then he would've come over
to ask you what happened.

56:26.800 --> 56:27.801
That's true.

56:30.386 --> 56:32.680
Did we buy too little?
Maybe we should've bought more.

56:33.223 --> 56:36.351
- You'll join us, right?
- I'll have to see.

56:37.727 --> 56:39.145
Gosh, do you miss him that much?

56:40.897 --> 56:43.650
- Call him and tell him to hurry home.
- He's at his parents' place.

56:44.234 --> 56:46.694
Their son has a date,
so I'm sure they'll let him leave.

56:46.986 --> 56:49.656
Talking about him is making me
miss him more. I'll head in first.

56:49.823 --> 56:50.657
Hey.

56:51.074 --> 56:53.535
What? Is she running in
to go see his empty place?

56:57.705 --> 56:59.749
She's totally crazy about him.

58:37.722 --> 58:38.806
It's okay.

58:45.563 --> 58:46.731
I'm okay, Hye-jeong.

58:51.277 --> 58:52.403
Yes, you should be.

59:09.504 --> 59:11.673
Hey, stop it.

59:20.348 --> 59:21.641
I feel...

59:22.809 --> 59:25.645
I feel like my heart is breaking into
pieces whenever I think about Eun-u.

59:30.400 --> 59:31.442
It hurts so much.

59:32.610 --> 59:34.362
It really drives me crazy.

59:43.663 --> 59:44.664
Hey.

59:46.457 --> 59:48.543
- You drank a lot. I'm sorry.
- Hi, Yeong-jae.

59:48.835 --> 59:49.919
Hey, Yeong-jae.

01:00:27.832 --> 01:00:30.043
Hey, Ji-ho. I'll take you home.

01:00:30.752 --> 01:00:33.921
No, wait. Hold on a moment, Yeong-jae.

01:00:34.005 --> 01:00:36.716
- What is it? Why?
- Hang on.

01:00:36.799 --> 01:00:38.217
- Let's go home.
- Wait!

01:00:38.885 --> 01:00:40.136
- I have to--
- What's the matter?

01:00:40.345 --> 01:00:43.181
- I have to go see Eun-u.
- You can go tomorrow.

01:00:43.264 --> 01:00:45.391
- Come on. Let's go.
- No, I have to go see Eun-u.

01:00:45.475 --> 01:00:48.061
- It's okay. Let's go.
- What?

01:00:48.144 --> 01:00:50.938
Just keep walking.
You can see him tomorrow.

01:00:53.983 --> 01:00:56.319
I'll take care of the rest.
You should call a taxi.

01:00:56.402 --> 01:00:57.695
I'll call one when I'm outside.

01:00:58.488 --> 01:01:00.948
Jeong-in, what about you?
Are you going to Ji-ho's place?

01:01:01.449 --> 01:01:02.533
Hold on.

01:01:03.743 --> 01:01:05.161
He hasn't read my messages yet.

01:01:05.578 --> 01:01:07.580
Are you already getting dumped or what?

01:01:11.000 --> 01:01:12.001
What was that sound?

01:01:12.627 --> 01:01:15.546
- Could that be Ji-ho?
- What? You think so?

01:01:26.683 --> 01:01:28.810
- I'll be right back.
- Hey, is it him?

01:01:30.478 --> 01:01:31.354
Jeong-in!

01:01:44.951 --> 01:01:46.744
Is Ji-ho all right?

01:01:47.537 --> 01:01:49.372
He's quite drunk.

01:02:02.969 --> 01:02:04.011
Ji-ho.

01:02:07.932 --> 01:02:09.934
Why did you drink so much?

01:02:15.148 --> 01:02:16.399
Did something happen?

01:02:23.489 --> 01:02:24.532
Jeong-in.

01:02:27.618 --> 01:02:28.786
Are you going to...

01:02:33.458 --> 01:02:34.667
leave us too?

01:03:15.208 --> 01:03:17.627
That was so unnecessary.
Why did you tell her that?

01:03:17.710 --> 01:03:19.879
Why did you show it
if you wanted to hide it?

01:03:19.962 --> 01:03:21.798
You went nuts.

01:03:21.881 --> 01:03:23.466
What if he's still hung up on her?

01:03:23.549 --> 01:03:26.803
I think I only saw
what was right in front of me.

01:03:26.886 --> 01:03:28.888
Are you going to put the blame on Ji-ho
and run away?

01:03:28.971 --> 01:03:31.057
I thought our love was all that mattered.

01:03:31.140 --> 01:03:34.185
I cluelessly thought I should be able
to understand everything...

01:03:34.936 --> 01:03:37.188
No, I didn't even think.

01:03:37.271 --> 01:03:38.981
I just assumed everything would work out.

01:03:39.065 --> 01:03:42.151
I think I need some time
to reflect on myself.

01:03:42.235 --> 01:03:43.569
Can you really accept me back?

01:03:43.653 --> 01:03:46.489
I betrayed you once. Do you think
you can still get back together with me?

01:03:46.614 --> 01:03:47.949
What if I betray you again?

01:03:48.324 --> 01:03:50.785
Be there for your buddy.
He already had it tough to begin with.

01:03:51.369 --> 01:03:52.245
Do you think you can

01:03:52.328 --> 01:03:54.080
get back together with Jeong-in
if I give up?

01:03:54.664 --> 01:03:55.665
I never said I would.

01:03:55.748 --> 01:03:58.042
You know me. My goal is taking you down.

01:04:00.711 --> 01:04:02.839
Subtitle translation by Hye-lim Park
